<paragraph id="2418850BFF1B83EBFF485CF5FD4AFA77" blockId="166.[112,766,1172,1484]" pageId="166" pageNumber="166">
<emphasis id="16D35919FF1B83EBFF485CF5FF5AFB57" box="[140,202,1173,1196]" italics="true" pageId="166" pageNumber="166">Notes.</emphasis>
– The systematic position of 
<taxonomicName id="E3A7FE88FF1B83EBFE3C5CF5FD01FB57" box="[504,657,1172,1196]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Brassica" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="166" pageNumber="166" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="nivalis">
<emphasis id="16D35919FF1B83EBFE3C5CF5FD01FB57" box="[504,657,1172,1196]" italics="true" pageId="166" pageNumber="166">Brassica nivalis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is controversial, and it has been assigned to at least five genera of the tribe 
<taxonomicName id="E3A7FE88FF1B83EBFFB45CB5FF41FB17" box="[112,209,1237,1260]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="166" pageNumber="166" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="tribe" tribe="Brassiceae">
<emphasis id="16D35919FF1B83EBFFB45CB5FF41FB17" box="[112,209,1237,1260]" italics="true" pageId="166" pageNumber="166">Brassiceae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Although some authors placed the species in 
<taxonomicName id="E3A7FE88FF1B83EBFD6F5CB5FF39FAF6" authority="Rouy" authorityName="Rouy" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Coincya" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="166" pageNumber="166" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="16D35919FF1B83EBFD6F5CB5FD6AFB17" box="[683,762,1237,1260]" italics="true" pageId="166" pageNumber="166">Coincya</emphasis>
Rouy
</taxonomicName>
(Greuter &amp; Burdet in 
<bibRefCitation id="4036F8FAFF1B83EBFE555C95FD1CFAF6" author="GREUTER, W. &amp; T. RAUS" box="[401,652,1269,1293]" pageId="166" pageNumber="166" pagination="79 - 99" refId="ref139260" refString="GREUTER, W. &amp; T. RAUS (ed.) (1983). Med-checklist notulae, 7. Willdenowia 13: 79 - 99." type="journal article" year="1983">GREUTER &amp; RAUS, 1983</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="4036F8FAFF1B83EBFD505C95FF4CFAD7" author="GREUTER, W. &amp; H. M. BURDET &amp; G. LONG" pageId="166" pageNumber="166" refId="ref139316" refString="GREUTER, W., H. M. BURDET &amp; G. LONG (1986). Med-checklist, a critical inventory of vascular plants of the circum-mediterranaean countries 3." type="journal volume" year="1986">GREUTER et al., 1986</bibRefCitation>
; 
<collectionCode id="42B61DCEFF1B83EBFF205D75FE81FAD6" box="[228,273,1301,1325]" country="Madagascar" httpUri="http://biocol.org/urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:13842" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:13842" name="Parc de Tsimbazaza" pageId="166" pageNumber="166" type="Herbarium">TAN</collectionCode>
, 2002) or in 
<taxonomicName id="E3A7FE88FF1B83EBFE545D74FDD3FAD7" authority="Andrz." authorityName="Andrz." box="[400,579,1300,1324]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Guenthera" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="166" pageNumber="166" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="16D35919FF1B83EBFE545D74FE66FAD7" box="[400,502,1300,1324]" italics="true" pageId="166" pageNumber="166">Guenthera</emphasis>
Andrz.
</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation id="4036F8FAFF1B83EBFD8B5D6FFF38FAB6" author="GOMEZ-CAMPO, C." pageId="166" pageNumber="166" pagination="301 - 307" refId="ref139157" refString="GOMEZ-CAMPO, C. (2003). The genus Guenthera Andr. in Bess. (Brassicaceae, Brassiceae). Anales Jard. Bot. Madrid 60: 301 - 307." type="journal article" year="2003">GÓMEZ-CAMPO, 2003</bibRefCitation>
, see comments under 
<taxonomicName id="E3A7FE88FF1B83EBFE655D55FDD0FAB7" box="[417,576,1333,1356]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Brassica" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="166" pageNumber="166" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="persica">
<emphasis id="16D35919FF1B83EBFE655D55FDD0FAB7" box="[417,576,1333,1356]" italics="true" pageId="166" pageNumber="166">Brassica persica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
), it is tentatively retained in 
<emphasis id="16D35919FF1B83EBFF2E5D35FED0FA97" box="[234,320,1365,1388]" italics="true" pageId="166" pageNumber="166">
<taxonomicName id="E3A7FE88FF1B83EBFF2E5D35FEACFA97" box="[234,316,1365,1388]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Brassica" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="166" pageNumber="166" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Brassica</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
as done by 
<bibRefCitation id="4036F8FAFF1B83EBFE7E5D35FD67FA96" author="LEADLAY, E. A. &amp; V. H. HEYWOOD" box="[442,759,1365,1389]" pageId="166" pageNumber="166" pagination="313 - 398" refId="ref140672" refString="LEADLAY, E. A. &amp; V. H. HEYWOOD (1990). The biology and systematics of the genus Coincya Porta &amp; Rigo ex Rouy (Cruciferae). Bot. J. Linn. Soc. 102: 313 - 398." type="journal article" year="1990">LEADLAY &amp; HEYWOOD (1990)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="4036F8FAFF1B83EBFFB55D15FEBEFA77" author="JALAS, J. &amp; J. SUOMINEN &amp; R. LAMPINEN" box="[113,302,1396,1421]" pageId="166" pageNumber="166" refId="ref140097" refString="JALAS, J., J. SUOMINEN &amp; R. LAMPINEN (ed.) (1996). Atlas Florae Europaeae 11. Cambridge University Press." type="book" year="1996">JALAS et al. (1996)</bibRefCitation>
, and 
<bibRefCitation id="4036F8FAFF1B83EBFEA25D15FD46FA77" author="WARWICK, S. I. &amp; I. A. AL-SHEHBAZ" box="[358,726,1396,1421]" pageId="166" pageNumber="166" pagination="237 - 248" refId="ref144724" refString="WARWICK, S. I. &amp; I. A. AL-SHEHBAZ (2006). Brassicaceae: chromosome number index and database on CD-Rom. Pl. Syst. Evol. 259: 237 - 248." type="journal article" year="2006">WARWICK &amp; AL-SHEHBAZ (2006)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="2418850BFF1B83EBFF485DF4FD77FA37" blockId="166.[112,766,1172,1484]" pageId="166" pageNumber="166">
The species does not fit in 
<taxonomicName id="E3A7FE88FF1B83EBFE505DF5FE72FA57" box="[404,482,1429,1452]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Coincya" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="166" pageNumber="166" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="16D35919FF1B83EBFE505DF5FE72FA57" box="[404,482,1429,1452]" italics="true" pageId="166" pageNumber="166">Coincya</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
because it drastically differs in floral morphology, geography, and chromosome numbers.
</paragraph>
